'''Flying Fish''' is a {{Rarity|Legendary}} fish found in the [[Ocean]].

== Description ==
{{Description|The Flying Fish is a unique fish, renowned for their wing-like fins which give them the ability to soar above the ocean's surface. They use this ability to swiftly evade predators as well as dwelling near the surface to find small organisms to feed on.|Bestiary Entry}}

